                            {
                                "text": "Tell me about benzoyl peroxide safety and whether I can mix it with retinol in my nighttime routine"
                            }
                        ],
                        "role": "user"
                    },
                    "final_response": {
                        "parts": [
                            {
                                "text": "Benzoyl peroxide is effective for acne treatment but can be drying. Mixing benzoyl peroxide with retinol is generally not recommended as they can deactivate each other and cause excessive irritation. Use them on alternate nights instead."
